title: "Did QE2 work?"
summary: CNBC featured Citi's Chief U.S. Equity Strategist Tobias Levkovich debating the impact of the Federal Reserve's quantitative easing program on the economy and markets with other analysts. Check out the segment, "Did QE2 Work?".
